    <chapter title="Engage" id="engage">
        <p>
            The ability to use Endurance to greatly increase the rate to block incoming
            attacks from a single enemy. This ability can not be used on an opponent that
            is currently under attack. Engage is received upon specializing in shields up
            to level 7.
