    <chapter title="Intercept" id="intercept">
        <p>
            The ability to take blows for someone else. Your character literally throws
            himself/herself in front of another character, sheilding that character with
            your body. Because of your recklessness, you will gain no bonuses from the
            armor you are wearing at the time you try to intercept. A shield is not
            required for this skill.
        </p>
    </chapter>

