    <chapter title="Parry" id="parry">
        <p>
            The ability to block a blow from your opponent using your weapon. This is an
            invaluable ability for those not using shields. The base chance to parry is 5%,
            and every time you train in parry, your chance to parry is increased by .5%.
        </p>
    </chapter>

    <chapter title="Protect" id="protect">
        <p>
            The ability for a tank class to guard a weaker class, reducing the enemy's
            aggro towards the weaker class, and transferring it onto the tank. This skill
            can be likened to a taunt. Only one Protect skill can be used on a character
            at a time. When multiple Protect skills are used the highest protect skill's
            value is used.
        </p>
        <chapter title="Protect I" id="protect-1">
            <p>The first level of protection a character receives.</p>
        </chapter>
        <chapter title="Protect II" id="protect-2">
            <p>Like Protect I, only you are better at it.</p>
        </chapter>
        <chapter title="Protect III" id="protect-3">
            <p>The most efficient protection a tank class can offer.</p>
        </chapter>
    </chapter>

